## Game Features:
Story: Justin wakes up in a medieval dungeon and must collect all 10 ancient artifacts from the dragons of wisdom.

Rooms: The game will have 20 rooms, including long hallways and special locations (like the dragonsâ€™ lairs).

Combat: Justin will encounter knights and castle guards along the way. Combat will be simple, turn-based, and could include health points for both the player and the enemies.

Items: There will be artifacts that Justin must collect, along with other items (potions, keys, weapons).

Ending: Once all 10 artifacts are found, Justin will be transported to a new world of paradise. ##

